      • removeButtonAction

        private void removeButtonAction()
        Action taken when the admin user removes a pokemon. If the textfield is empty then it returns a error in a form of a label; if he inputs something then the method checks if the pokemon is present or not, if it does than the Pokemon is removed, otherwise the methods shows an error up as a label.
